name: Aether Dust: Fire Planet
description: According to legend, the fifth element aether is the invisible material that fills the empty space of the universe. Inspired by mythical utopias and medieval sciences, Aether Dust is a digital universe comprised of multiple planets and moons. In this digital realm, time doesn’t exist, the seasons are altered and new elements are created often. Each planet is governed by a specific element, and is protected by its inhabitants to maintain bountiful natural splendor and harmony.
